WEBVTT

00:00:01.036 --> 00:00:04.476
The wheel was invented a long time ago,

00:00:04.476 --> 00:00:05.636
but we’re way behind.

00:00:06.916 --> 00:00:09.236
Hi, my name is Jane Velkovski.

00:00:09.796 --> 00:00:11.796
I’m 13 years old,

00:00:11.796 --> 00:00:13.796
a student in a public school

00:00:13.796 --> 00:00:15.516
and a passionate football fan.

00:00:16.316 --> 00:00:17.796
In addition to that,

00:00:17.796 --> 00:00:19.796
I’m a kid with a disability.

00:00:20.516 --> 00:00:23.756
My condition is known as SMA:

00:00:23.756 --> 00:00:25.956
spinal muscular atrophy,

00:00:25.956 --> 00:00:30.356
where the muscles are getting weak
but the brain remains strong.